%% RAG ingestion + Q&A end-to-end flow
%% Render: https://mermaid.live/
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant FE as 🌐 Frontend
    participant GW as 🟦 Gateway
    participant DOC as ☕ Documents
    participant MINIO as 📦 MinIO
    participant REDIS as 🔴 Redis Streams
    participant PROC as 🦀 Processing
    participant AI as 🐍 AI Engine
    participant QD as 🧭 Qdrant
    participant LLM as 🤖 LLM
    participant RT as 🟨 Realtime

    Note over User,RT: ━━━ PHASE 1: UPLOAD (sync REST) ━━━
    User->>FE: PDF seç + yükle
    FE->>GW: POST /api/v1/documents (multipart)
    GW->>DOC: POST /documents
    DOC->>MINIO: PUT object (tenant/<uuid>/file.pdf)
    DOC->>DOC: Tika parse → text + metadata
    DOC->>DOC: Postgres INSERT (RLS otomatik tenant_id)
    DOC-->>GW: 202 Accepted {job_id, doc_id}
    GW-->>FE: 202 Accepted
    DOC->>REDIS: XADD doc.uploaded.v1 {doc_id, tenant_id, ...}

    Note over User,RT: ━━━ PHASE 2: INGESTION (async) ━━━
    REDIS-->>PROC: XREADGROUP doc.uploaded
    PROC->>PROC: Semantic chunk (paragraph + sentence)
    PROC->>PROC: tantivy BM25 index update
    PROC->>REDIS: XADD doc.chunked.v1 {doc_id, chunks[]}
    REDIS-->>AI: XREADGROUP doc.chunked
    AI->>AI: sentence-transformers embed each chunk
    AI->>QD: upsert vectors (tenant_id payload)
    AI->>REDIS: XADD doc.ready.v1 {doc_id}

    Note over User,RT: ━━━ PHASE 3: STATUS PUSH (server push) ━━━
    REDIS-->>RT: XREADGROUP doc.ready
    RT->>FE: WebSocket: {type: doc_ready, doc_id}
    FE->>User: Toast "Doküman hazır"

    Note over User,RT: ━━━ PHASE 4: QUESTION (sync + SSE + gRPC) ━━━
    User->>FE: "Geçen yılki gelirimiz neydi?"
    FE->>GW: POST /api/v1/chat (SSE)
    GW->>AI: POST /chat
    AI->>AI: agent loop başlat
    AI->>LLM: prompt + tool definitions
    LLM-->>AI: tool_use: doc_search("gelir 2025")
    AI->>AI: embed query
    AI->>QD: dense search → top-20
    AI->>PROC: gRPC BM25Search → top-20
    AI->>AI: Reciprocal Rank Fusion → top-5
    AI->>AI: cross-encoder rerank → top-3
    AI->>LLM: tool_result: 3 chunks + kaynak ref
    LLM-->>AI: token stream başlar
    loop her token
        AI->>REDIS: XADD llm.token.streamed.v1
        REDIS-->>RT: XREADGROUP llm.token.streamed
        RT->>FE: WebSocket: {type: token, text: "..."}
        FE->>User: anlık token render
    end
    LLM-->>AI: stop
    AI->>REDIS: XADD llm.token.streamed.v1 {type: done, sources: [...]}
    RT->>FE: WebSocket: {type: done, sources}
